# Claude Workflow configuration reference
#
# Use `claude-workflow config` for common model, reasoning, and permission
# settings. This file documents advanced and provider-specific overrides.
#
# Put trusted user-wide overrides in ~/.claude-workflow.env. The legacy
# ~/.ultrathink.env file is read afterward for upgrade compatibility.
# Workflow entrypoints deliberately ignore a repository .env unless the parent
# shell exports CLAUDE_WORKFLOW_LOAD_PROJECT_ENV=true.

# Main/frontier route. [1m] is a Claude Code client alias; the gateway sends the
# plain upstream model id to Anthropic.
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_MAIN_MODEL_ID=claude-fable-5[1m]
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_MAIN_PROVIDER=anthropic
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_MAIN_UPSTREAM_MODEL=claude-fable-5
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_ANTHROPIC_PASSTHROUGH_MODELS=claude-fable-5*

# Workflow/subagent route exposed to Claude Code and resolved through Codex.
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_SUBAGENT_MODEL_ID=claude-sonnet-5
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_SUBAGENT_UPSTREAM_MODEL=gpt-5.6-terra
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_SUBAGENT_REASONING_EFFORT=max
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_SUBAGENT_VERBOSITY=high
# CLAUDE_WORKFLOW_DISPLAY_ROUTED_MODEL=true
# CLAUDE_WORKFLOW_SUBAGENT_MODEL_ID=codex-terra

# Permission bypass is the intentional launcher default. Use it only in trusted
# repositories and machine environments. Set false to restore Claude prompts.
# CLAUDE_WORKFLOW_SKIP_PERMISSIONS=false
# This opt-in must be exported by the parent shell; a project .env cannot enable itself.
# CLAUDE_WORKFLOW_LOAD_PROJECT_ENV=false

# Per-launch gateway. Leave the port unset/0 for an isolated dynamic port.
# The standalone raw gateway defaults to 4319; the managed daemon defaults to 4318.
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_HOST=127.0.0.1
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_PORT=0
# The shell daemon manager reads these values from its parent environment before
# the Node gateway loads this file. Export manager overrides in your shell rc;
# use absolute paths or $HOME rather than a literal ~ inside a variable value.
# export ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_DAEMON_PORT=4318
# export CLAUDE_WORKFLOW_GATEWAY_STATE_DIR="$HOME/.cache/claude-workflow"
# export CLAUDE_WORKFLOW_GATEWAY_ENV_FILE="$HOME/.cache/claude-workflow/claude-workflow-gateway.env"

# Non-loopback binds require gateway authentication. With a shared secret, a
# static Anthropic key is also required for Anthropic passthrough because the
# inbound Claude credential is consumed by the gateway.
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_SHARED_SECRET=change_me
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.anthropic.com
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_ANTHROPIC_VERSION=2023-06-01

# Codex app-server route. The command is the executable only; the gateway adds
# `app-server`. The shared daemon requires Codex CLI 0.144.1 or newer because
# it starts dynamic-tools-only threads with no native execution environment.
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_ENABLED=true
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_COMMAND=codex
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_CWD=/absolute/path/to/project
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_SANDBOX=workspace-write
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_APPROVAL_POLICY=never
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_MODEL=gpt-5.6-terra
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_REASONING_EFFORT=max
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_VERBOSITY=low

# Context/session limits. Workflow sessions default both byte caps to 0 so the
# current Codex app-server owns token-aware tool-output truncation; positive
# values opt back into gateway transport caps.
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_INPUT_MAX_TOKENS=180000
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_AUTO_COMPACT_TOKEN_LIMIT=126000
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_AUTO_COMPACT_TOKEN_LIMIT_SCOPE=body_after_prefix
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_TOOL_RESULT_MAX_BYTES=0
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_TOOL_RESULT_WINDOW_MAX_BYTES=0
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_IDLE_TIMEOUT_MS=120000
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_FORK_IDLE_TIMEOUT_MS=30000
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_PENDING_TOOL_TIMEOUT_MS=600000
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_CODEX_MAX_SESSIONS=16

# Optional tracing. For the shared daemon, export the trace directory from the
# parent shell because the shell manager selects it before this file is loaded.
# Use an absolute path or off/false/no/0. Existing custom directories must be
# mode 0700; trace files are mode 0600 and rotate at 8 MiB / three files.
# export ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_TRACE_DIR="$HOME/.cache/claude-workflow/gateway-trace"
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_TRACE_MAX_BYTES=8388608
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_TRACE_MAX_FILES=3

# Refusal fallback. When set, Fable/Mythos-family passthrough requests opt into
# Anthropic's server-side refusal fallback (beta server-side-fallback-2026-06-01):
# a safety-classifier decline (stop_reason: refusal) is transparently re-served by
# this model in the same call. If Anthropic rejects the param, the gateway retries
# once without it, so the option can never break requests. Unset = off.
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_REFUSAL_FALLBACK=claude-opus-4-8

# Optional direct OpenAI-compatible route (primarily compatibility/testing).
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_OPENAI_MODEL=your-approved-openai-model
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_OPENAI_REASONING_EFFORT=low
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_OPENAI_VERBOSITY=low

# Optional DeepSeek main route.
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your_deepseek_api_key
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_DEEPSEEK_MODEL=deepseek-v4-pro
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_DEEPSEEK_REASONING_EFFORT=max

# Optional GLM/Z.ai main route.
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_GLM_API_KEY=your_zai_api_key
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_GLM_BASE_URL=https://api.z.ai/api/coding/paas/v4
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_GLM_MODEL=glm-5.2
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_GLM_REASONING_EFFORT=max
# ULTRATHINK_THINKING_LEVEL=HIGH

# Exact entries win over wildcard route-map entries. Exact entries also become
# the default /v1/models discovery list.
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_ROUTE_MAP_JSON='{"claude-sonnet-5":{"provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.6-terra","sandbox":"workspace-write","approvalPolicy":"never","reasoningEffort":"max","verbosity":"high","displayName":"Codex Terra"}}'
# ULTRATHINK_GATEWAY_EXPOSED_MODELS=claude-fable-5[1m],claude-sonnet-5,codex-terra

# Corporate proxy support. The launcher adds its local host to NO_PROXY/no_proxy.
# HTTPS_PROXY=http://proxy.example.com:8080
# HTTP_PROXY=http://proxy.example.com:8080
# ALL_PROXY=http://proxy.example.com:8080
# NO_PROXY=localhost,127.0.0.1
